Turn tibble into gt Table with Custom Formatting

Source: R/tables.R
mygt.Rd

Formatting includes:

  • Text align to top/left

  • Smaller row padding

  • No top border

  • Bold column labels

mygt(df)

Arguments

df

Data frame/tibble

Value

Formatted gt table

Examples

data(mtcars)
mtcars %>%
  dplyr::slice(1:5) %>%
  mygt()
